data.title: Happy Habitoween!
data.text: For this spooky celebration, you've received a Jack-O-Lantern Pet and an assortment of candy for your Pets!

data.title: Happy Harvest Feast!
data.text: Gobble gobble, you've received the Turkey Pet!

data.title: It’s Habitica’s Birthday!
data.text: Celebrate with us and enjoy these Absurd Party Robes, delicious cake, and 20 Gems!
